  * security_getprocattr() - Read an attribute for a task
  * @p: the task
- * @lsm: LSM name
+ * @lsmid: LSM ID
  * @name: attribute name
  * @value: attribute value
  *
@@ -3829,13 +3829,13 @@ EXPORT_SYMBOL(security_d_instantiate);
